  "title": "WSH OFFICER CUM ECO",
  "description": "<p><u>A. Main Responsibilities</u></p>\n<p>1.</p>\n<p>Set up safety and Environmental standards and procedures for the Group Companies &amp; when necessary, revise or modify such procedures to improve safety in the workplace.</p>\n<p>2.</p>\n<p>Conduct regular site inspections and follow-up actions to ensure safety and environmental compliance.</p>\n<p>3.</p>\n<p>Implement, train &amp; educate all management, staff, workers &amp; sub-contractors on safety and environmental measures and enforcements.</p>\n<p>4.</p>\n<p>Assist with incident investigation.</p>\n<p>5.</p>\n<p>Maintain emergency response plan on environment, health and safety.</p>\n<p>6.</p>\n<p>Application safety award and Consass audit</p>\n<p>7.</p>\n<p>Other ad-hoc duties assigned from time to tim</p>",
